<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/201746-does-the-story-have-a-good-ending-i-still">Does the story have a good ending? I still enjoy a story where the virtuous of heart ultimately triumph over adversity. I supposes it gives u a sense of hope in a world that at times seems somewhat dire.

Cheers
Paul</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
