<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/26391750-sandra"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1416434394i/26391750._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/26391750-sandra">Sandra</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I am currently studying this novel at University, and my professor explained that in a conference in Barcelona he asked Toni Morrison how did the nove<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I am currently studying this novel at University, and my professor explained that in a conference in Barcelona he asked Toni Morrison how did the novel end. Her answer was 'do you want my version?', and then she admitted that to her it was a good ending, a hopeful ending, as you say.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
